OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783797589
OL,3,CPlans for 30 'affordable homes'
OL,4,Capproved on appeal
OL,6,FPlans for 30 designated affordable
OL,7,Fhomes on the edge of St Martin's
OL,8,FVillage in Jersey have been approved
OL,9,Fon appeal.
OL,11,FThey were initially refused in March
OL,12,Fdue to concerns around road safety,
OL,13,Fwaste drainage systems and car parking.
OL,15,FHowever, 18 three-bed and 12 two-bed
OL,16,Fproperties will now be built by the
OL,17,FDandara Group on a field on La Rue Des
OL,18,FButtes, at the edge of the village.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
