OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783797589
OL,3,CPlans for 30 'affordable homes'
OL,4,Capproved on appeal
OL,6,FIn total, 16 of the properties will be
OL,7,Fearmarked for affordable purchase by
OL,8,Ffirst-time buyers and the other 14
OL,9,Fwill be social rented housing,
OL,10,Ftransferred to the Jersey Homes Trust.
OL,12,FEight of the homes will be
OL,13,Fspecifically dedicated for low-income
OL,14,Fparishioners.
OL,16,FThe initial planning refusal was
OL,17,Fappealed by Dandara and overturned
OL,18,Fafter the inspector was satisfied and
OL,19,FAssistant Environment Minister,
OL,20,FSenator Sir Mark Boleat, agreed to the
OL,21,Fdecision.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783797589
OL,3,CPlans for 30 'affordable homes'
OL,4,Capproved on appeal
OL,6,FIt was concluded the scheme will now
OL,7,Fdeliver a wider highway alongside
OL,8,Fimproving access for all road users.
OL,10,FThe developer has agreed to a #247,000
OL,11,Finfrastructure contribution, that will
OL,12,Finclude junction realignment and
OL,13,Ftraffic calming, as well as a bus
OL,14,Fshelter and local bus service
OL,15,Fimprovements.
OL,17,FThe plans will also include communal
OL,18,Fpublic open spaces and a traffic-free
OL,19,Fwoodland walk.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783797589
OL,3,CPlans for 30 'affordable homes'
OL,4,Capproved on appeal
OL,6,FThere were also concerns about sewer
OL,7,Finfrastructure. Dandara now says that
OL,8,Fit will install on-site sewage tanks
OL,9,Funtil the planned Maufant storage
OL,10,Fupgrade is completed. That is expected
OL,11,Fto take place by 2031.
OL,13,FParking concerns had also been raised
OL,14,Fby the Parish. Jersey's zone-specific
OL,15,Fplanning laws require 36 spots and the
OL,16,Fdevelopment now promises 40, alongside
OL,17,F67 bicycle spaces.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
