PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1783797589
OL,3,CPlans for 30 'affordable homes'
OL,4,Capproved on appeal
OL,6,FOn that basis, the build is set to go
OL,7,Fahead subject to conditions and a
OL,8,F'Planning Obligation Agreement'. That
OL,9,Fdocument is a legally enforceable
OL,10,Fmechanism to ensure that the site
OL,11,Fremains designated as affordable.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
